        "# Hybrid Fraud Detection System Using Supervised and Unsupervised Learning\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook implements a hybrid fraud detection system using machine learning techniques.\n",
        "\n",
        "Methods used:\n",
        "- SMOTE for class imbalance\n",
        "- Isolation Forest for anomaly detection\n",
        "- Random Forest\n",
        "- Logistic Regression\n",
        "- Gradient Boosting\n",
        "\n",
        "Evaluation metrics:\n",
        "- Precision\n",
        "- Recall\n",
        "- F1-score\n",
        "- ROC-AUC"
      ],
